OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfcom lays out new rules   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor TikTok and Twitch      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%title3
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ofcom has laid out the measures it will
OL,6, require video-sharing platforms to take
OL,7, to better protect users.               
OL,9,FThe VSPs, including TikTok, Snapchat,  
OL,10,FVimeo and Twitch, must ensure content  
OL,11,Frelated to terrorism, child sexual     
OL,12,Fabuse and racism does not appear.      
OL,14,FA third of users have seen hateful     
OL,15,Fcontent on such sites, Ofcom says.     
OL,17,FAnd the regulator will fine VSPs that  
OL,18,Fbreach its new mandatory guidelines or 
OL,19,F- in the most serious cases - suspend  
OL,20,Fthe service entirely.                  
